Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.97,0:00:02.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吾向比斯科帝宣战
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.98,0:00:03.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而米露茜接受了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.77,0:00:07.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一如既往的战争
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.15,0:00:08.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.73,0:00:11.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吾一定会保护到底
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.19,0:00:13.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论是国家还是人民
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.53,0:00:14.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抑或是你们的明天
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.57,0:00:16.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出发吧 库兰贝尔
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.07,0:00:18.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将你的力量借于吾
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.48,0:02:02.98,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(520,0)\fs55\blur4\3c&H3B5D92&\fsp2\pos(984,710)}「格兰纳据点攻防战」
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.31,0:01:58.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾奥殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.52,0:02:00.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实在对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.31,0:02:05.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,碧欧蕾姐姐大人和近卫狮团的任务失败了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.40,0:02:11.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐大人和近卫狮团都在斯里兹据点内被抓住
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.37,0:02:14.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是么 高尔那边怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.29,0:02:18.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按照您的命令 和格德文将军还有杰诺华兹一起
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.96,0:02:19.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赶往斯里兹据点
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.58,0:02:28.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 高尔殿下他们对这次的战争好像提不起什么兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.97,0:02:29.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无妨
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.63,0:02:34.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽力打出华丽一战 与将士们尽情享受就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.85,0:02:38.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吾会一人取胜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.44,0:02:48.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次的战争违背道义
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.78,0:02:50.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为是命令所以去攻击据点
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.70,0:02:52.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 随便应付了事就行
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.53,0:02:54.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.91,0:02:56.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,格德文 我也对不起你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.62,0:02:59.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让你做这种无聊之事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.62,0:03:00.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您说什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.66,0:03:05.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能同殿下同行 我已经没什么怨言了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.88,0:03:06.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.34,0:03:07.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高尔殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.84,0:03:10.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,据先遣部队的消息说
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.97,0:03:14.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米露茜欧莱公主殿下不在斯里兹据点
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.80,0:03:18.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样就能安心的攻陷据点了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.85,0:03:22.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被人说在大战中偷懒的话 我也会很没面子的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.15,0:03:26.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就相应地认真耍耍吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.20,0:03:33.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是 查帕鲁湖沼地带
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.36,0:03:36.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总数三万人的决战
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.50,0:03:37.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于开始
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.41,0:03:40.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战斗区域的点数是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.16,0:03:43.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,5100比4900
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.33,0:03:45.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比斯科帝稍占优势
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.63,0:03:48.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 局势还不明朗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.00,0:03:51.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是通往格兰纳浮游据点的必经之路
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.55,0:03:56.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比斯科帝的第二部队刚刚进入我们的视线
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.93,0:03:58.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是奇袭骑兵部队
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.10,0:04:01.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以非常快的速度在前进
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.19,0:04:12.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 穿过此桥本阵就在眼前了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.95,0:04:14.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鼓起干劲不断攻过去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.91,0:04:17.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.45,0:04:23.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞬光 连天炮
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.34,0:04:37.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然还是不行么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.18,0:04:40.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始撤退 撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.56,0:04:46.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,达尔琪安卿
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.15,0:04:50.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骑士团长发来的作战指示
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.98,0:04:51.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.74,0:04:55.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望达尔琪安卿和帕尼托尼的第三部队
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.86,0:04:58.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,支援前方的第二部队
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.24,0:05:00.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.54,0:05:05.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌阵开始散乱了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.29,0:05:07.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突破过去比较快些吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.21,0:05:11.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尤吉卡泽 比斯科帝第三部队全员
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.30,0:05:13.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟上在下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.84,0:05:16.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突破敌阵 支援第二部队
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.68,0:05:19.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战况有所变化
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.80,0:05:21.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,达尔琪安卿麾下的第三部队
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.68,0:05:23.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始由守转攻
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.43,0:05:28.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对向蕾奥阁下本阵进攻的第二部队进行支援吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.15,0:05:29.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.28,0:05:37.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等下 达尔琪安卿
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.20,0:05:41.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久不见 巴纳德将军
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.49,0:05:42.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久疏问候
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.20,0:05:46.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实在抱歉 这里不能让你们过去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.42,0:05:51.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以认为 这是你要单挑我的意思吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.25,0:05:53.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不会觉得我这是无礼的请求
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.71,0:05:54.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请务必同意
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.68,0:05:59.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请稍等
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.51,0:06:04.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴纳德 单挑的话我来奉陪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.93,0:06:05.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罗兰
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.98,0:06:07.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马尔狄诺基卿
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.94,0:06:10.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战况一变再变
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.73,0:06:12.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然要变成指挥官的对决了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.65,0:06:16.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两军骑士团长的对决么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.88,0:06:20.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思啊 这里就交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.74,0:06:22.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你去吧 达尔琪安卿
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.08,0:06:24.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.70,0:06:27.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第三部队 出发了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.12,0:06:28.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.21,0:06:34.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 和你多久没单挑了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.84,0:06:38.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自从我们都担任骑士团长之后的第一次
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.63,0:06:41.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经三年多了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.93,0:06:44.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两人都生于骑士家庭
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.01,0:06:50.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,私底下也是经常联系 互赠礼物的好朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.48,0:06:52.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两军的骑士团长
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.52,0:06:55.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚至坐骑西鲁库尔也都是名骑的对决
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.15,0:06:58.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且两人的武器也都是枪与盾
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.90,0:07:00.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧 两军骑士团长
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.45,0:07:02.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,堵上自己的荣誉战斗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.04,0:07:13.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.38,0:07:16.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是斯里兹据点
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.05,0:07:17.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.09,0:07:21.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以高尔殿下为首的亲卫队攻击真是厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.60,0:07:30.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虎牙双拳
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.91,0:07:47.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弓箭部队 放箭
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.88,0:07:57.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,触碰
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.34,0:08:06.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,右侧防御阵 击退完成
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.47,0:08:08.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将军 麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.81,0:08:18.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人数的优势根本不值一提
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.32,0:08:23.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中央的比斯科帝守卫们像落叶般飘落
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.71,0:08:35.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样 首席
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.08,0:08:36.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.08,0:08:39.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 乘着风势
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.34,0:08:41.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该可以一下子飞起来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.30,0:08:46.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈兰 一起去公主殿下那里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.85,0:08:53.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乘骑哈兰和学院炮术师莉歌塔{\fnsimhei}·{\r}艾尔玛尔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.15,0:09:01.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出击
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.24,0:09:09.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会让你去的 放箭
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.96,0:09:16.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好危险
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.21,0:09:18.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1 2
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.81,0:09:37.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.10,0:09:39.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓓尔队长 前面！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.25,0:10:02.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杰诺华兹弓箭部队 击破
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.13,0:10:06.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能浪费首席宝贵的牺牲
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.85,0:10:18.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得救了 哈兰
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.44,0:10:22.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么重整精神
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.45,0:10:25.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赶快到公主殿下和勇者大人那里去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.61,0:10:28.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过在此之前要去哪弄件衣服呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.53,0:10:34.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是格兰纳浮游据点前
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.99,0:10:39.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比斯科帝的第二部队马上就要进入据点守卫的攻击范围内了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.17,0:10:41.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,守护本阵的部队
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.79,0:10:45.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按照蕾奥阁下的战略 配置了特战装备部队
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.55,0:10:48.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特战装备部队？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.52,0:10:50.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主殿下 请移动到大家的中央
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.93,0:10:51.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.72,0:10:55.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一波要来了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.93,0:11:00.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,列防守阵 散开前进 保护好公主
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.60,0:11:06.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,炮术师队 枪兵部队 准备
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.53,0:11:10.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,枪？ 大炮？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.57,0:11:14.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇者 之前教给你的纹章术
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.70,0:11:15.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以正确的用出来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.79,0:11:17.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前的是哪个
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.20,0:11:19.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,枪的那个？ 盾的那个？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.25,0:11:20.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盾的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.33,0:11:23.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你来防御 我来突破
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.42,0:11:25.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.80,0:11:28.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Defender
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.12,0:11:32.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发射
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.14,0:11:42.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,炮术师 对准勇者发射
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.73,0:11:43.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.02,0:11:47.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发射
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.87,0:12:05.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什 什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.96,0:12:09.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇者真红把炮弹弹开了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.21,0:12:11.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样 艾克蕾
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.22,0:12:14.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 得瑟
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.09,0:12:16.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过正好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.60,0:12:24.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闪空
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.31,0:12:28.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一字巨斩
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.25,0:12:42.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骑士团 收拾残军！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.83,0:12:45.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真厉害 真厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.17,0:12:48.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇者真红和亲卫队长艾克蕾尔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.96,0:12:50.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞬间将门前守卫击破
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.88,0:12:52.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始向据点内部进军
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.88,0:12:55.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要变天了么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.08,0:12:59.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从东边的天空飘来一些乌云
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.62,0:13:26.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不见星辰的阴天
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.87,0:13:28.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却能看到令人讨厌的画面
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.17,0:13:31.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是据点的武斗台么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.55,0:13:39.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要哭泣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.43,0:13:41.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我止住眼泪 米露茜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.89,0:13:47.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让你悲伤之事 令你痛苦之物…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.14,0:14:22.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,师傅大人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.64,0:14:26.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,木叶 是在据点的方向吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.64,0:14:31.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 达尔琪安卿 帕尼托尼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.61,0:14:32.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个声音究竟是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.32,0:14:37.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊那个 是像危险警报一样的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.82,0:14:42.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有使一般参加的兵士们无法享受战争乐趣的危险
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.12,0:14:45.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让在下先去排除危险
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.12,0:14:48.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,部队的带领和指挥就交给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.04,0:14:49.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.17,0:14:53.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从这个反应看
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.63,0:14:55.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是个相当棘手的家伙么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.23,0:14:59.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给弗洛尼亚大地带来灾难的魔物
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.84,0:15:03.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有时会将整个国家烧成焦土
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.23,0:15:10.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有时甚至将神杀死的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.81,0:15:11.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不祥之物
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.42,0:15:34.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是让吾等的不耐烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.42,0:15:37.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那里的是勇者和垂耳吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.01,0:15:45.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吾正在此据点的最上部
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.14,0:15:47.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天空武斗台
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.35,0:15:50.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为你们能到达这里的奖励
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.64,0:15:52.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赐予你们与吾单挑的机会
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.61,0:16:00.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,库兰贝尔和埃克斯玛姬娜也都在此
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.61,0:16:02.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若能夺走
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.11,0:16:07.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就分数而言你们的胜利就是板上钉钉的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.62,0:16:10.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然 逐个交战的话你们不是对手
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.95,0:16:14.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两个人也无妨 最好一起上
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.34,0:16:19.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吾将打败你们 夺走帕拉迪奥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.67,0:16:23.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在此之后 再去摧毁米露茜的部队
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.93,0:16:26.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 快上来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.52,0:16:36.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾奥阁下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.77,0:16:39.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？ 我没事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.07,0:16:40.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要在此等候
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.69,0:16:45.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毫不知情的勇者和垂耳就会把帕拉迪奥带来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.86,0:16:48.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仅仅因此星象就会改变也说不定
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.70,0:16:50.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.92,0:17:00.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来 明明是国家大战之日
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.50,0:17:01.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天公却如此不作美
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.39,0:17:15.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扰了 蕾奥米谢莉阁下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.52,0:17:24.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾奥阁下不惜以国家的宝剑作为赌注战斗的话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.53,0:17:28.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得我也必须手持宝剑来此
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.66,0:17:31.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擅自出战 多有得罪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.58,0:17:35.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.17,0:17:37.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为何 为何会
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.04,0:17:40.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾奥米谢莉阁下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.88,0:17:42.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论如何请告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.17,0:17:44.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这场战争的真正理由
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.92,0:17:48.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾奥阁下心中真实的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.43,0:17:57.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鲁修 我现在正在和蕾奥阁下…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.65,0:17:59.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,责备的话之后有的是机会
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.61,0:18:03.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 现在没有时间向您说明了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.45,0:18:08.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将这个夺走的话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.84,0:18:31.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果能对我说明实情
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.80,0:18:35.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把宝剑借给您多少次都可以
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.10,0:18:43.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 为什么蕾奥阁下什么都不对我说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.99,0:18:50.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前明明关系那么好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.20,0:18:53.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直温柔地对待我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.62,0:18:57.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不只是宝剑
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.91,0:18:59.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就连最近的几次战争也是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.67,0:19:05.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾奥阁下 蕾奥阁下就那么讨厌我吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.34,0:19:07.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吾…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.56,0:19:21.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷静点 勇者
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.19,0:19:23.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不像样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.27,0:19:25.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾克蕾不也是 尾巴
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.57,0:19:31.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烦死了 公主殿下说要一个人去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.07,0:19:33.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也只好等着了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.78,0:19:38.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过总有不祥的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.08,0:19:42.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎样 从我们这里没法操纵升降机吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.25,0:19:45.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚刚确认了下 是锁住的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.34,0:19:50.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾克蕾 过来下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.76,0:19:55.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉可以从这边过去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.81,0:19:57.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像真的能过去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.68,0:20:00.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过勇者 公主殿下她…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.48,0:20:03.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是 公主殿下说的是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.86,0:20:10.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从这里开始就让我一个人过去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.32,0:20:17.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以从这里上去就完全没问题了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.12,0:20:19.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小孩子么你是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.87,0:20:22.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愿意的话可以不上来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.21,0:20:24.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一个人也会上去的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.29,0:20:28.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁说不上去了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.76,0:20:35.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向正在进行格兰纳浮游据点攻防战的大家发出通知
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.47,0:20:41.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在雷云的影响下 附近的弗洛尼亚之力略有减弱
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.35,0:20:44.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 因为还有雷击的危险
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.40,0:20:49.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以请大家暂时停止战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.44,0:20:50.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重复一遍
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.99,0:20:52.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战斗暂时停止
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.36,0:20:56.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs36}请到安全的场所避难
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.36,0:20:58.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 两位也请到有屋顶的地方来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.46,0:21:12.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾克蕾
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.31,0:21:19.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米露茜
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.68,0:21:21.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾奥阁下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.06,0:21:29.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾奥阁下 米露茜大人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.15,0:21:31.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这 这究竟是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.23,0:21:36.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,格兰纳据点著名的天空武斗台好像正在升空
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.61,0:21:38.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看那边
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
